flowchart TD
    Start[Server Action Started] --> TryBlock[Enter try block]

    TryBlock --> CheckAuth[Check user authentication\ngetUserId()]

    CheckAuth -->|Throws| CatchBlock[Go to catch block]

    CheckAuth -->|Success| MainLogic[Execute main logic\ncreate / update / delete]

    MainLogic -->|Success| SuccessReturn[Return { success: true, data }]
    MainLogic -->|Fails| CatchBlock

    CatchBlock --> HandleError[handleActionError(error)]

    HandleError --> IsKnown{Is this a known error?}

    IsKnown -->|Yes| SpecificMessage[Return specific friendly message]
    IsKnown -->|No| GenericMessage[Return generic error message]

    SpecificMessage & GenericMessage --> LogError[console.error]
    LogError --> ReturnError[Return { success: false, error: 'message' }]

    SuccessReturn --> End[Action completes]
    ReturnError --> End